artview.plugins.PhaseProcLp.phase_proc_lp¶

PhaseProcLp.phase_proc_lp()[source]¶

Mount Options and execute phase_proc_lp. The resulting fields are added to Vradar. Vradar is updated, strong or weak depending on overwriting old fields.
